programme.desc: Peter Jackson nos ofrece una nueva versión de este clásico del cine. Durante la Gran Depresión, Ann Darrow, una actriz de vodevil, se queda sin trabajo. Su suerte parece cambiar cuando conoce a Carl Denham, un empresario que lucha para abrirse camino en el mundo del espectáculo. A ellos se une Jack Driscoll, un autor de teatro. Los tres emprenden un viaje a una remota isla, donde Denham tiene previsto dirigir una película. En una frondosa selva, descubren a King Kong, un gorila gigantesco, y a una tribu de seres prehistóricos que han vivido ocultos durante millones de años.

programme.title: Spider-Man: Un nuevo universo

programme.title: Iron Man

programme.title: Al límite del riesgo

programme.title: Un talento increíble

programme.title: Nigeria’s Miracle Baby Scammers
programme.desc: Africa Eye goes undercover to expose the fertility scammers targeting Nigerian women and fuelling an underground trade in black market babies. Women with fertility issues in Nigeria are being tricked into parting with hundreds of?dollars, duped into believing they?re pregnant and delivering babies that are often trafficked. Africa Eye's undercover investigation exposes one of these scammers, a woman known as Dr Ruth, who guarantees results but says delivery won?t happen without payment for an expensive ?drug?.?The documentary investigates how these scammers prey on women so desperate for a baby that they?believe or choose to ignore the reality that is obvious to most.? We speak to those who have fallen for this scam?and expose the link to baby trafficking. Yemisi Adegoke reports on the crippling stigma of infertility in Nigeria and exposes the criminal networks who profit from it.

programme.title: Pet Sematary
programme.desc: Massachusetts doctor Louis Creed moves to a small Maine town with his wife Rachel, their kids, Ellie and Gage, and Church, the cat. While exploring the local woods, Ellie stumbles across a funeral procession of children taking a dead dog to a cemetery. Neighbour Jud Crandall warns the Creeds that the woods are dangerous, as they soon discover for themselves via the dark power of the local burial ground. Horror based on the Stephen King novel, starring Jason Clarke, Amy Seimetz and John Lithgow

programme.title: Dora and the Lost City of Gold
programme.desc: Having spent most of her life exploring the jungle with her parents, nothing could prepare Dora for her most dangerous adventure ever - high school. Always the explorer, Dora quickly finds herself leading Boots (her best friend, a monkey), Diego, a mysterious jungle inhabitant and a rag tag group of teens on a live-action adventure to save her parents and solve the impossible mystery behind a lost city of gold. Live-action adaptation of the hit animated kids' show, starring Isabela Merced, Eva Longoria and Jeff Wahlberg

programme.title: Daleks' Invasion Earth: 2150 AD
programme.desc: Eccentric time traveller the Doctor journeys into the future, where he finds his arch enemies the Daleks have taken over the Earth and are hatching an evil scheme to remove the planet's core and turn it into a vast spaceship. Sci-fi adventure sequel based on the TV series, starring Peter Cushing, Bernard Cribbins, Andrew Keir, Roberta Tovey and Ray Brooks

programme.title: Secret Headquarters
programme.desc: Fourteen-year-old Charlie Kincaid yearns for a deeper connection to his father Jack, who frequently disappears at short notice for work. When an IT conference interrupts Charlie's birthday, the teenager invites friends to a party at his father's house, and they stumble upon a subterranean, gizmo-laden lair. Comedy adventure, starring Owen Wilson, Walker Scobell and Michael Pena

programme.title: The Seeker: The Dark Is Rising
programme.desc: A teenager discovers he is the last in a long line of warriors destined to defend the world from dark forces. His duty now is to embark on a perilous journey through time to recover the six parts of a powerful mystical artefact and ensure it is returned to safe hands. Fantasy adventure, starring Alexander Ludwig, Christopher Eccleston and Ian McShane

programme.title: We Live in Time Interview Special
programme.desc: Stars Andrew Garfield and Florence Pugh - along with director John Crowley - talk about making the Film4-backed romantic drama We Live in Time

programme.title: Taxi
programme.desc: A bumbling New York cop is unable to pursue a gang of bank robbers in their souped-up getaway car because he does not have a driving licence. Fortunately, help is on hand in the form of a taxi driver with dreams of becoming a racing driver, and whose customised cab is the fastest in New York. Comedy adventure remake, starring Queen Latifah, Jimmy Fallon and Gisele Bundchen

programme.title: The Mechanic
programme.desc: A professional hitman lets his emotional detachment slip when his mentor is murdered, and puts his deadly skills to the task of getting revenge. The solitary assassin finds an ally in his teacher's son, who also yearns for vengeance and persuades the killer to teach him the tricks of the trade. Action thriller remake, starring Jason Statham, Ben Foster and Donald Sutherland.

programme.title: No Exit
programme.desc: Stranded at an isolated highway rest stop in the mountains, a college student discovers a kidnapped child hidden in a car belonging to one of the people inside. Thriller, starring Havana Rose Liu, Danny Ramirez, David Rysdahl and Dennis Haysbert

programme.title: Bull
programme.desc: After a decade away, gangland enforcer Bull returns to the streets where he used to do the bidding of his father-in-law, sadistic mob boss Norm. The men fell out when Norm's daughter Gemma developed a drug addiction and Bull demanded sole custody of their son, Aiden. Bull's return ignites the fuse on an orgy of violence targeted at the crime lord and his minions. Thriller, starring Neil Maskell, David Hayman and Tamzin Outhwaite

programme.title: Slice
programme.desc: A pizza delivery driver is murdered on the job, so the city searches for someone to blame. Could it be drug dealers, ghosts or even a werewolf? Horror comedy, starring Chris Parnell, Paul Scheer, Rae Gray and Chance the Rapper

programme.title: Enemy Mine
programme.desc: In the midst of a war between humans and aliens, two space pilots from opposite sides are marooned together on an inhospitable planet and are forced to set aside their mutual animosity to survive. Sci-fi adventure, starring Dennis Quaid, Louis Gossett Jr and Brion James

programme.title: It Came from Beneath the Sea
programme.desc: The captain of a nuclear submarine battles a gigantic octopus threatening to destroy San Francisco. Monster adventure, starring Kenneth Tobey, Faith Domergue and Donald Curtis, with special effects by Ray Harryhausen

programme.title: Decision at Sundown
programme.desc: A gunslinger rides into a backwoods town intent on finding his dead wife's former lover and exacting revenge for her death. The man he blames now has total control of the town and has the sheriff at his beck and call. Undeterred, the drifter offers his enemy an ultimatum - he has until sundown to leave the town or face retribution for his crimes. Western, with Randolph Scott, John Carroll and Andrew Duggan

programme.title: Picnic
programme.desc: A drifter turns up in a small American town looking for a well-off old friend in the hope of borrowing money. However, he causes nothing but trouble for the locals, seducing both his old pal's fiancee and a local schoolteacher. Drama based on William Inge's Pulitzer Prize-winning play, starring William Holden, Cliff Robertson and Kim Novak

programme.title: Flight of the Phoenix
programme.desc: The crew and passengers of a cargo plane are left stranded in the Gobi desert after a crash. They embark on a desperate plan to return to civilisation - by building a new plane out of the wreckage of the old one. Action adventure remake, starring Dennis Quaid, Tyrese Gibson, Giovanni Ribisi, Miranda Otto and Hugh Laurie

programme.title: We Live in Time Interview Special
programme.desc: Stars Andrew Garfield and Florence Pugh - along with director John Crowley - talk about making the Film4-backed romantic drama We Live in Time

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
programme.desc: Secret agent Ethan Hunt and his team are implicated in a bombing at the Kremlin, forcing the American president to declare them fugitives. The spies plan to clear their name by abducting the real terrorist, which leads them into a pursuit around the globe. However, Hunt cannot be sure his colleagues are trustworthy. Action adventure sequel, starring Tom Cruise, Jeremy Renner, Simon Pegg and Paula Patton

A British soldier deployed to Belfast in 1971, almost immediately finds himself caught up in a riot. In the aftermath, he becomes separated from the rest of his unit. Lost and alone at night in a hostile and unfamiliar area, he makes a disturbing journey in search of safety. Thriller, starring Jack O'Connell and Richard Dormer

programme.title: Snatched
programme.desc: After being dumped by her boyfriend before their holiday, Emily Middleton takes her cautious mother Linda with her to Ecuador. However, their lives are soon turned upside down when the pair are kidnapped. Fish-out-of-water comedy, starring Amy Schumer, Goldie Hawn and Joan Cusack

programme.title: Cover Girl
programme.desc: Dancer Rusty Parker works in a small New York club with her choreographer boyfriend Danny McGuire, but gets a taste of fame when she wins a competition to appear on the cover of a prestigious magazine. This in turn leads to her starring in hit musical, though her success has a dramatic effect on her relationship with Danny. Musical comedy, starring Rita Hayworth and Gene Kelly

programme.title: Tora! Tora! Tora!
programme.desc: Fact-based Second World War drama recounting the bombing of Pearl Harbour from both the Japanese and American perspectives, reconstructing the events leading up to the devastating attack on the US naval base in 1941. Starring Martin Balsam, So Yamamura, Joseph Cotten, James Whitmore and Jason Robards

programme.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
programme.desc: An explorer discovers a prehistoric monster-infested world deep beneath Earth's crust and faces a tough ordeal escaping the predatory attacks of the creatures as he tries to guide his team back to safety. Sci-fi adventure based on Jules Verne's novel, starring Pat Boone, James Mason, Arlene Dahl and Diane Baker

programme.title: Deep Impact
programme.desc: A TV reporter investigating a presidential misdemeanour stumbles on evidence that a comet is on a collision course with Earth, threatening the future of the human race. Meanwhile, an astronaut prepares to lead his crew on a do-or-die mission to intercept the danger. Sci-fi drama, starring Robert Duvall, Tea Leoni, Morgan Freeman and Elijah Wood

programme.title: The G
programme.desc: A mysterious woman seeks revenge on the corrupt legal guardian who destroyed her life. Crime thriller, starring Dale Dickey, Romane Denis and Daniel Brochu

programme.title: The Drop
programme.desc: A Brooklyn bartender secretly provides a service delivering shipments of money to local gangsters. His criminal connections lead to his involvement in a robbery that goes disastrously wrong and digs up the long-buried secrets from his neighbourhood's past. programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Part 2 of 2. Cobra's s plot proves to be working… until Destro discovers a duplicate of himself constructed by Cobra commander. The angered Destro takes information on the synthoids to the only people on Earth who can stop Cobra: G.I. Joe.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Leatherneck attends graduation ceremonies at a new academy and discovers it is run by Buck McCann, the leader of Cobra's own Marine Corps. Leatherneck must foil McCann's plan to destroy Paris Island Marine Academy.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Cobra commander hires a gypsy to summon the spirits of three great warriors from the past. Once in control of the ghosts, he commands them to destroy G.I. Joe. But the Baroness, now relieved of her duties, tells the Joes how to eliminate the threat.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: The Joes go Hollywood as technical advisers on a movie about their special-missions unit. But when the filmmakers attempt to use a captured Cobra stinger, Cobra Commander has another idea for the movie's ending.

programme.title: Shaun The Sheep
programme.desc: Shaun the Sheep, selalu saja ada masalah baik dari kawanan domba sendiri ataupun dari peternak yang membuat Shaun "turun tangan" menyelesaikan masalah tersebut.

programme.title: Upin & Ipin

Candida Leaver is extremely displeased when she experiences a sleepless night, while Sue Perkins and Gill take the opportunity to go out and have some fun

programme.title: Four in a Bed

programme.title: Four in a Bed
programme.desc: The contestants meet one last time to learn how much they have been paid by their fellow hoteliers before discovering who has won the week's competition. Old tensions resurface as the results are announced, and there are heated exchanges around the table

programme.title: Car S.O.S.
programme.desc: Tim Shaw and Fuzz Townshend head to Rochdale to rescue an Opel Manta GTE. The car belongs to former amateur rally driver Alan, who loved his Manta so much he couldn't bear to part with it, even when it went off the road. With Alan becoming a bit of a recluse after developing health problems and losing his wife to cancer, his family and friends hope that the Car S.O.S treatment will be just the thing to bring Alan back out of his shell

programme.title: Car S.O.S.
programme.desc: Tim Shaw and Fuzz Townshend head to Dorset to pick up a Ford Escort MK2 RS2000, which belongs to carpenter Mike. After his son was involved in a horrific road accident, Mike gave up work and supported him through a four-year recovery. Now, Mike's family want to give something back to offer thanks to such a devoted father by presenting him with his fully restored RS2000

programme.title: PopMaster TV
programme.desc: Ken Bruce returns for a celebrity special as five famous faces put their music knowledge to the test. programme.title: Yorkshire by the Sea
programme.desc: Documentary following the lives of locals living along Yorkshire's coastline. This episode features members of the Robson family from Bridlington, who've been fishing the North Sea for generations, as they head up the coast to Whitby for a boat repair. Volunteers at Bempton Cliffs work to protect and preserve almost half a million seabirds, and a group of sea swimmers take a full-moon sea swim at Scarborough

programme.title: Emergency
programme.desc: A mum of three is rushed to St Mary's with a femur fracture and broken knee after a car crash and 15 year-old Louie recovers from surgery to repair an artery in his leg after he kicked a glass door at school. London's Air Ambulance team arrive on scene after 20 year-old motorcyclist Tyler collides with a car, they find serious injuries to his right leg, jaw and arm and blood coming out of his ear. Lance Corporal Lee has surgery to bring his spine and pelvis back into the right position after a paragliding accident

Quemar después de leer
programme.desc: Un CD con las memorias de un agente de la CIA cae en manos de dos empleados de un gimnasio, no muy listos, que intentarán venderlo al mejor postor.

programme.title: Un tipo serio
programme.desc: De la mano de los hermanos Coen nos llega esta celebrada comedia nominada a dos Premios Óscar incluyendo el de mejor película. Con un humor áspero y una brillante interpretación de Michael Stuhlbarg, sigue la debacle vital de un neurótico profesor de física cuya vida se pone patas arriba de la noche a la mañana. Medio-oeste americano, 1967. Larry Gopnik es un profesor de física que ve cómo de la noche a la mañana su vida se derrumba. Es un hombre bueno, un marido fiel y afectuoso, un buen padre y un profesor serio, pero, de repente, todo en su vida empieza a ir mal. Su mujer lo abandona sin explicaciones, y el amante de ella lo convence para que deje su casa y se mude a un motel por el bien de los niños. Además, su carrera profesional se ve amenazada cuando comienza a recibir una serie de anónimos con acusaciones contra su persona.

programme.title: Delicatessen
programme.desc: En un inmenso descampado se alza un viejo edificio habitado por personas de costumbres más bien extrañas, que sólo tienen una preocupación: alimentarse. El propietario es un peculiar carnicero que tiene su establecimiento en los bajos del bloque.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E01: Episodio 1
programme.desc: Es el último día de Sarah como jefa de investigación en el departamento de homicidios. Está a punto de despedirse e informar a su sustituto de los casos pendientes, cuando recibe un inquietante envío.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E02: Episodio 2
programme.desc: Los peores temores de Theis y Pernille se han hecho realidad. Su hija de 19 años, Nanna, ha aparecido torturada y asesinada. Los detalles del caso están por esclarecerse.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E03: Episodio 3
programme.desc: Sarah y Jan están convencidos de que conocen el paradero de John Lynge, a quien busca la policía. Jan no quiere esperar refuerzos y su reticencia afecta a la investigación.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E04: Episodio 4
programme.desc: Sarah y Jan han localizado una habitación en el sótano del instituto con restos de drogas, sangre y algunas prendas de Nanna que indican que allí ocurrió algo violento.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E05: Episodio 5
programme.desc: Algo indica que Sarah y Jan deberían desviar su atención de los estudiantes del instituto y dirigirla en otra dirección. Las cosas mejoran para Troels y su campaña.

programme.title: ¡Ay, Carmela!
programme.desc: Cansados de pasar penalidades, unos cómicos que animan a los soldados republicanos, viajan a Valencia, donde por error van a parar a la zona nacional.

programme.title: Un plan para enamorarse (Amor, boda y matrimonio)
programme.desc: Ava lo tenía todo: amor, felicidad y una boda preciosa. Es consejera matrimonial y su trabajo consiste en ayudar a los demás, pero su vida se trastoca cuando descubre que el 'feliz matrimonio' de sus padres, está a punto de acabar en divorcio.

programme.title: Pequeñas mentiras para estar juntos
programme.desc: Max, arruinado y algo deprimido, regresa a su casa de verano para venderla. Sus viejos amigos, que han pasado en ella grandes momentos juntos, aparecerán por sorpresa en su cumpleaños.

programme.title: Un diván en Túnez
programme.desc: Después de estudiar durante varios años en Francia, Selma abre su propia consulta psiquiátrica en un popular suburbio de Túnez, justo después de la Primavera árabe.

programme.title: Minari. Historia de mi familia
programme.desc: David, un niño coreano americano de siete años, ve cómo a mediados de los años 80 su vida cambia de la noche a la mañana cuando su padre decide mudarse junto a toda la familia a Arkansas.

programme.desc: Wladyslaw Szpilman, un brillante pianista polaco judío, escapa de la deportación durante el asedio nazi. Obligado a vivir en el corazón del gueto de Varsovia, comparte el sufrimiento, la humillación y las miserias del resto de prisioneros.

programme.title: Juegos sucios
programme.desc: Craig, un padre de familia en plena crisis económica, ahoga sus penas en un bar cuando un desconocido le propone un trato: le dará cierta cantidad de dinero si va cumpliendo una serie de acciones.

programme.title: El secreto de sus ojos
programme.desc: Durante 25 años, un crimen ha permanecido, imborrable, en la memoria de benjamín espósito.Ahora, en su madurez, decide volver sobre esa historia; recorrer de nuevo aquel pasado de amor, muerte y amistad.

programme.desc: Grace Kelly, una gran estrella de Hollywood, renunció a su carrera como actriz para casarse en 1956 con el príncipe Rainiero III y convertirse en Su Alteza Serenísima la Princesa Gracia de Mónaco.

programme.desc: Troels se mete en un lío cuando alguien de su departamento intenta ocultar que uno de los profesores de Nanna se vio envuelto en una historia con una joven alumna.

programme.desc: Justo cuando Jan cree que ya está a cargo de la investigación del crimen, Sarah regresa. Está muy preocupada porque Theis ha desaparecido con Rama.

programme.desc: Con la ayuda del imán local, Sarah y Jan encuentran el lugar donde se aloja el ayudante de Rama y hacen algunos descubrimientos que refuerzan las sospechas contra éste.

programme.desc: Sarah y Jan están estancados en su investigación, y su jefe les da 24 horas para obtener información concluyente, o les apartará del caso.

programme.desc: Sarah y Jan siguen una nueva y decisiva pista, pero se ven sorprendidos por la intervención de su jefe. El hecho de que Sarah haya ignorado las órdenes de su superior tendrá consecuencias.

programme.desc: Lucien de Rubempré, joven poeta de clase baja, está locamente enamorado de la baronesa Louise de Bargeton. El riesgo de escándalo los obliga a huir a París.

programme.title: Cinema Paradiso
programme.desc: Salvatore, un director de cine, sufre una fuerte conmoción cuando le comunican la muerte de Alfredo, su viejo amigo proyeccionista. Esa noche no duerme al revivir su infancia y juventud.

programme.title: Única superviviente
programme.desc: El 24 de agosto de 1981, los recién casados Larisa y Vladimir Savitsky suben a bordo de un avión para volver de su luna de miel. 30 minutos antes del aterrizaje, el avión sufre un accidente.

programme.title: Complete Unknown
programme.desc: Tom organiza una cena y uno de sus compañeros de trabajo llega con una intrigante cita llamada Alice. Tom está convencido de que la conoce, pero ella se niega a reconocer su historia.

programme.desc: June tiene la intención de pasar los primeros días de la pandemia en el norte del estado con su novio, John. Pero sus planes se ven frustrados cuando John decide quedarse en Nueva York.

programme.desc: En 1947, Seretse Khama, el rey de Botswana, conoció a Ruth Williams, una oficinista londinense. La atracción fue inmediata.

programme.title: The Killing: Crónica de un asesinato - T1, E11: Episodio 11
programme.desc: Sarah ha encontrado la vivienda de la que Nanna tenía la llave. El apartamento pertenece a los Liberales, y muestra signos de una pelea a vida o muerte con evidencias claras de la presencia de Nanna.

programme.desc: La policía y Troels Hartmann están convencidos de que Olav Kristensen sabe quién ha estado implicado en la muerte de Nanna, pero ahora Olav está muerto.
